            <div class="main_r">
                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1790" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0109</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8672 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成都南湖国际社区物业品牌内涵提炼的故事：基于精细化管理的实践与探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Case Study: The Story of Brand Connotation Determining Process for Chengdu South Lake Property Co., </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">艾进，张梦等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成都森宇物业有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">现代物业；精细化管理；业主满意度；服务质量感知价值；品牌内涵；统计方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Modern Property Management Industry; Brand Connotation,; Lean Management; Property Owners’ Satisfaction; Perceived Values of Service Quality; Statistic Methods</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了成都南湖国际社区物业管理公司在面对一系列日常管理困境中如何利用现代服务运作管理的手段，以业主满意度调查为工具，以精细化管理为理念，同时获得控制人工成本、提升服务品质和提高业主满意度，提炼并塑造其品牌的管理实践过程。案例由提出问题，分析问题和解决问题的基本框架进行信息的整合与描述。由此，本案例首先主要用于学生讨论和分析现代物业管理企业的现状和问题以及未来战略，并由此涉及企业流程化与规范化管理等精细化管理理论的核心问题。随后本案例导入了精细化管理中细节化与个性化管理内容在南湖国际社区管理公司日常管理实践与品牌内涵提炼工作中的具体决策与过程，并引导学生进行相关的提炼与思考。同时，本案例还涉及到了品牌定位，管理调研，业主满意度测量以及服务质量感知价值的识别与测量等相关专业知识，并引导学生通过科学的研究与决策方法来对企业精细化化管理的过程与细节进行更为深入的评价与解读。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case gives a great detail about how a property management company deals with its problems and dilemma of its daily work, by using the tool of property owners’ satisfaction surveys under the thoughts and rules of lean management concept. This case also demonstrates how the company, Chengdu South Lake, during this management process, by determining its brand connotation, archives the deduction of overall labor costs, while having perceived service quality improvement and higher owners’ satisfaction levels in the same time. By doing so, this case, then presents the inner relationships between customer perceived values and daily management tasks of a service company, and reveals traits about the management practices of China’s private companies. By discussing the information about the property management industry and the problems on hand of Nanhu, students firstly, will be asked to discuss the current conditions of Nanhu, the major problems and threats, as well as its opportunities. Thus, strategy evaluation tools will be introduced here with key concepts about lean management, the standardizing and processing management. By using the information about how the company comes up to and carries on its decisions，students will be asked to design an owners’ satisfaction survey, by using core concepts, such as perceived service quality values, customer satisfaction, and post-purchasing behavioral intentions from managerial courses. At last, by displaying Nanhu’s movements after its survey study, students will have the understanding about how lean management concept can be used in a real business condition, how the brand connotation determining tasks can be done by lean management process, and how tasks should be conducted in the process of daily management, while students can give more in-depth options by summarizing and digging the data from the survey study.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《品牌管理》、《管理学（企业管理）》、《服务运作管理》、《旅游企业管理》、《不动产经营管理》、《管理研究方法》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子表格模型、阴影价格</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
